   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>On Mesore 10, has brought Severinus, of the villagers of Karanis, for the sixteenth indiction, one-hundred and twenty litrai of chaff, 120 litrai [only]. I, Ision, have signed.</ab>
